卷舍引擎的多 Agent 写作管线与 "truth files"（真相文件）连续性架构
衍生自以下上游项目，特此致谢：

This work is derived from, and gratefully acknowledges, the following
upstream project:

    InkOS — Autonomous novel-writing AI Agent
    Author:     Narcooo
    Repository: https://github.com/Narcooo/inkos
    License:    GNU AGPL-3.0-only

InkOS 开创了 Radar → Planner → Composer → Architect → Writer → Observer
→ Auditor → Reviser 的自主写作 Agent 管线，以及独立于 LLM 生成、用于长篇
连续性管控的 "truth files" 架构。卷舍引擎在此基础之上继续开发。

InkOS pioneered the autonomous writing-agent pipeline (Radar → Planner →
Composer → Architect → Writer → Observer → Auditor → Reviser) and the
"truth files" architecture for long-form continuity. Juanshe Engine builds
upon that foundation.


